  "title": "Retail Supervisor",
  "description": "<h2><strong>✨ Retail Supervisor ✨</strong></h2><h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>Take your retail career to the next level! We are looking for an experienced and motivated <strong>Retail Supervisor</strong> to lead our store teams, deliver excellent customer service, and support store performance.</p><h3><strong>📍 Work Locations</strong></h3><p>• Ang Mo Kio (AMK)<br />• Bedok</p><h3><strong>💼 Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><p>• Lead, supervise, and support retail staff in daily operations<br />• Train and onboard new team members and develop staff skills<br />• Deliver excellent customer service and handle customer feedback professionally<br />• Manage store opening and closing procedures and ensure operational standards<br />• Monitor stock levels and coordinate with inventory team<br />• Support Store Manager in achieving sales targets and KPIs<br />• Ensure compliance with company policies and procedures</p><h3><strong>✅ Job Requirements</strong></h3><p>• Minimum high school diploma or equivalent (Bachelor’s degree in Retail, Business, or related field is an advantage)<br />• Relevant retail experience; supervisory experience preferred<br />• Strong leadership, communication, and interpersonal skills<br />• Customer-focused, proactive, and well-organised<br />• Able to work weekends and public holidays<br />• Familiar with EPOS systems and retail management software</p><h3><strong>🎁 Benefits & Salary</strong></h3><p>• <strong>Salary up to $3,000/month + Supervisor Commission</strong><br />• Medical benefits and annual leave<br />• Annual company trip and store incentive schemes</p><h3><strong>⏰ Working Hours</strong></h3><p><strong>Full-Time:</strong><br />• <strong>AMK:</strong><br />  5-Day Work Week (11:00 AM – 9:00 PM, 2-hour break)<br />  6-Day Work Week option available<br />• <strong>Bedok:</strong><br />  5-Day Work Week (8:30 AM – 5:30 PM, 1-hour break)<br />  6-Day Work Week option available</p><p><strong>Part-Time (if applicable):</strong><br />• $10/hour<br />• $12/hour on Public Holidays<br />• Minimum commitment: 3 days per week</p><h3><strong>📩 How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume/CV to:<br />📧 <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">hr@uonegolive.com</a></p>",
